@FinanceAPI_HostAddress = http://localhost:5097
@ContentType = application/json

### ========================
### Authentication
### ========================

### 一般使用者登入
# @name loginUser
POST {{FinanceAPI_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: {{ContentType}}

{
  "username": "user1",
  "password": "123456"
}

> {%
client.global.set("userToken", response.body.accessToken);
%}

###

### 管理者登入
# @name loginAdmin
POST {{FinanceAPI_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: {{ContentType}}

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "123456"
}

> {%
client.global.set("adminToken", response.body.accessToken);
%}

###

### 登入失敗
POST {{FinanceAPI_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: {{ContentType}}

{
  "username": "wrong-user",
  "password": "wrong-password"
}

###

### ========================
### User Happy Path
### ========================

### 查詢可存取帳戶清單
GET {{FinanceAPI_HostAddress}}/api/accounts
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

###

### 查詢帳戶資料
GET {{FinanceAPI_HostAddress}}/api/accounts/1
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

###

### 查詢帳戶餘額
GET {{FinanceAPI_HostAddress}}/api/accounts/1/balance
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

###

### 查詢帳戶交易明細
GET {{FinanceAPI_HostAddress}}/api/accounts/1/transactions
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

###

### 存款
POST {{FinanceAPI_HostAddress}}/api/accounts/1/deposit
Content-Type: {{ContentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

{
  "amount": 1000.00
}

###

### 提款
POST {{FinanceAPI_HostAddress}}/api/accounts/1/withdraw
Content-Type: {{ContentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

{
  "amount": 500.00
}

###

### 轉帳
POST {{FinanceAPI_HostAddress}}/api/transfers
Content-Type: {{ContentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

{
  "fromAccountId": 1,
  "toAccountId": 3,
  "amount": 500.00
}

###

### 查詢單筆交易紀錄
GET {{FinanceAPI_HostAddress}}/api/transactions/1
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

###

### 條件查詢交易紀錄
GET {{FinanceAPI_HostAddress}}/api/transactions?accountId=1&type=Deposit
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

###

### ========================
### Authorization Tests
### ========================

### 未登入查詢帳戶
GET {{FinanceAPI_HostAddress}}/api/accounts/1
Accept: application/json

###

### 一般使用者查詢不屬於自己的帳戶
GET {{FinanceAPI_HostAddress}}/api/accounts/999
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

###

### 一般使用者查詢其他帳戶的交易紀錄
GET {{FinanceAPI_HostAddress}}/api/transactions?accountId=999
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

###

### 一般使用者查詢轉帳紀錄列表
GET {{FinanceAPI_HostAddress}}/api/transfers?accountId=1
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

###

### 一般使用者查詢單筆轉帳紀錄
GET {{FinanceAPI_HostAddress}}/api/transfers/1
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

###

### ========================
### Admin Happy Path
### ========================

### 管理者查詢所有帳戶
GET {{FinanceAPI_HostAddress}}/api/accounts
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### 管理者查詢交易列表
GET {{FinanceAPI_HostAddress}}/api/transactions?accountId=1
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### 管理者查詢轉帳紀錄列表
GET {{FinanceAPI_HostAddress}}/api/transfers?accountId=1
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### 管理者查詢單筆轉帳紀錄
GET {{FinanceAPI_HostAddress}}/api/transfers/1
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### ========================
### Validation Tests
### ========================

### 存款金額等於 0
POST {{FinanceAPI_HostAddress}}/api/accounts/1/deposit
Content-Type: {{ContentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

{
  "amount": 0
}

###

### 存款金額小於 0
POST {{FinanceAPI_HostAddress}}/api/accounts/1/deposit
Content-Type: {{ContentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

{
  "amount": -100
}

###

### 提款金額等於 0
POST {{FinanceAPI_HostAddress}}/api/accounts/1/withdraw
Content-Type: {{ContentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

{
  "amount": 0
}

###

### 轉帳來源與目標相同
POST {{FinanceAPI_HostAddress}}/api/transfers
Content-Type: {{ContentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

{
  "fromAccountId": 1,
  "toAccountId": 1,
  "amount": 100.00
}

###

### 轉帳金額等於 0
POST {{FinanceAPI_HostAddress}}/api/transfers
Content-Type: {{ContentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

{
  "fromAccountId": 1,
  "toAccountId": 2,
  "amount": 0
}

###

### 轉帳帳戶編號無效
POST {{FinanceAPI_HostAddress}}/api/transfers
Content-Type: {{ContentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

{
  "fromAccountId": 0,
  "toAccountId": 0,
  "amount": 100.00
}

###

### 轉帳金額格式錯誤
POST {{FinanceAPI_HostAddress}}/api/transfers
Content-Type: {{ContentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

{
  "fromAccountId": 1,
  "toAccountId": 2,
  "amount": "abc"
}

###

### ========================
### Business Error Tests
### ========================

### 查詢不存在的帳戶
GET {{FinanceAPI_HostAddress}}/api/accounts/999999
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### 查詢不存在的餘額
GET {{FinanceAPI_HostAddress}}/api/accounts/999999/balance
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### 查詢不存在的帳戶交易
GET {{FinanceAPI_HostAddress}}/api/accounts/999999/transactions
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### 對不存在的帳戶存款
POST {{FinanceAPI_HostAddress}}/api/accounts/999999/deposit
Content-Type: {{ContentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "amount": 1000.00
}

###

### 對不存在的帳戶提款
POST {{FinanceAPI_HostAddress}}/api/accounts/999999/withdraw
Content-Type: {{ContentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "amount": 1000.00
}

###

### 提款超過餘額
POST {{FinanceAPI_HostAddress}}/api/accounts/1/withdraw
Content-Type: {{ContentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

{
  "amount": 99999999.00
}

###

### 查詢不存在的轉帳紀錄
GET {{FinanceAPI_HostAddress}}/api/transfers/999999
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### 查詢不存在的交易紀錄
GET {{FinanceAPI_HostAddress}}/api/transactions/999999
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

